headline: Expeditors (NYSE:EXPD) Surprises With Strong Q3
summary: Logistics and freight forwarding company Expeditors (NYSE:EXPD) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, but sales fell by 3.5% year on year to $2.89 billion. Its GAAP profit of $1.64 per share was 17.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
